summary: An ordinance declaring certain buildings Nos. 2508 Forrest Street, 1706-8 Terry Avenue, 4835 24th Avenue Southwest, 4508 East 50th Street, 518 Fairview Avenue North, 3104 Jameson Street, 2857 22nd Avenue West, 2221 West Barrett Street and 711 3rd Avenue West, to be public nuisances, and directing the institution of legal proceedings to procure the abatement thereof.
